tps://soundcloud.com/harpersmagazine">SoundCloud</a> , <a href="https://www.stitcher.com/podcast/harpers-magazine/the-harpers-podcast">Stitcher</a> , <a href="https://www.deezer.com/us/show/3364832">Deezer</a> , or <a href="https://open.spotify.com/show/4h9SICTDppd1iJv9n5jXfc?si=zzWUGj8vQfaDJlzDaxmnwg">Spotify</a> .</h3><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org/2023/07/the-doomsday-machine/">The Doomsday Machine</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://harpers.org">Harper&#39;s Magazine</a> .</p> ]]>;</content:encoded><wfw:commentrss> https://harpers.org/2023/07/the-doomsday-machine/feed/</wfw:commentrss><slash:comments> 0</slash:comments></item></channel></rss>